The collision, between a taxi and a sedan, happened 10km from Hendrina. The four men travelling in the sedan were thrown from the car when the two vehicles crashed.
They were certified dead on the scene. Joseph Shaka, Evans Muthemwa and Shammy Chititare will be buried in Zimbabwe. The paper could not reach the family of Ashley Manenzanis before print. Two women that were travelling in the taxi were transported to the hospital, while the driver of the taxi sustained minor injuries.